OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780434671
OL,3,CFuneral held for soldier who died at
OL,4,CRoyal Windsor Horse Show
OL,6,FThe funeral has taken place for the
OL,7,Fsoldier who died after falling from
OL,8,Fher horse at the Royal Windsor Horse
OL,9,FShow.
OL,11,FFamily, friends, regimental senior
OL,12,Fstaff and military colleagues filled
OL,13,FThe Guards' Chapel, Wellington
OL,14,FBarracks, in central London, to pay
OL,15,Ftheir respects to Lance Bombardier
OL,16,FCiara Sullivan.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
