OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780434671
OL,3,CFuneral held for soldier who died at
OL,4,CRoyal Windsor Horse Show
OL,6,FThe 24-year-old, who was part of the
OL,7,FKing's Troop, Royal Horse Artillery,
OL,8,Fsuffered serious injuries after
OL,9,Ffalling on May 15 at around 7pm after
OL,10,Fexiting the arena. She died at the
OL,11,Fscene.
OL,13,FState trumpeters from The Band of the
OL,14,FHousehold Cavalry played fanfares as
OL,15,Fthe coffin, draped in the Union flag,
OL,16,Farrived.
OL,18,FHer coffin travelled by gun carriage
OL,19,Ffrom The Royal Mews to The Guards'
OL,20,FChapel.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780434671
OL,3,CFuneral held for soldier who died at
OL,4,CRoyal Windsor Horse Show
OL,6,FA three-round volley was also fired in
OL,7,FWellington Barracks, after which L/Bdr
OL,8,FSullivan's personal items, including
OL,9,Fher cap and medals, were presented to
OL,10,Fher family.
OL,12,FL/Bdr Sullivan's horse Neymar carried
OL,13,Fher riding boots reversed in its
OL,14,Fstirrups, as a traditional military
OL,15,Fmark of respect signalling her final
OL,16,Fjourney.
OL,18,FAnd flags flew at half-mast at all
OL,19,FArmy buildings in London in her honour.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
