OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780434671
OL,3,CFuneral held for soldier who died at
OL,4,CRoyal Windsor Horse Show
OL,6,FFloral tributes spelled out "Sully",
OL,7,Fthe name she was called by friends,
OL,8,Fand were surrounded by photographs of
OL,9,Fher in uniform riding her horse.
OL,11,FShe was deployed at the late Queen's
OL,12,Fstate funeral in 2022 and the
OL,13,Fcoronation of Charles and Camilla the
OL,14,Ffollowing year.
OL,16,FA Buckingham Palace spokesman said
OL,17,Fpreviously that the King was "greatly
OL,18,Fshocked and saddened" to learn of L/
OL,19,FBdr Sullivan's death and that he would
OL,20,Fbe in touch with her family to share
OL,21,Fhis condolences.
OL,26,@nD@]OUnD@cO]yD@^OUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
