FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780434671
OL,3,CFuneral held for soldier who died at
OL,4,CRoyal Windsor Horse Show
OL,6,FL/Bdr Sullivan, who was said to love
OL,7,Fhorses and have a natural affinity for
OL,8,Fthem, was remembered previously by her
OL,9,Fcommanding officer as an "exceptional
OL,10,Fjockey" with an "infectious energy".
OL,12,FHer commanding officer said in a
OL,13,Ftribute issued by the Ministry of
OL,14,FDefence (MoD): "Lance Bombardier (L/
OL,15,FBdr) Ciara Sullivan, 'Sully' to her
OL,16,Ffriends, was to all who had the
OL,17,Fprivilege of serving alongside her, a
OL,18,Fbright light in any room she entered.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@GO]rD@QOUrD@cO]vD@POU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780434671
OL,3,CFuneral held for soldier who died at
OL,4,CRoyal Windsor Horse Show
OL,6,F"An immensely professional soldier and
OL,7,Fan exceptional jockey, she approached
OL,8,Fevery day within The Troop with an
OL,9,Finfectious energy ` the kind that
OL,10,Flifted those around her without effort
OL,11,For intention ` and was unfailingly
OL,12,Fpresent for her comrades in both the
OL,13,Fsmall moments and the hard ones."
OL,15,FCharles and members of the royal
OL,16,Ffamily were present at the arena at
OL,17,Fthe time the incident took place but
OL,18,Fwere not made aware of the severity of
OL,19,Fthe situation until later, the
OL,20,FBuckingham Palace spokesman said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
