OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780434671
OL,3,CFuneral held for soldier who died at
OL,4,CRoyal Windsor Horse Show
OL,6,FL/Bdr Sullivan joined the Army
OL,7,FTraining Centre in Pirbright, near
OL,8,FWoking, Surrey, in November 2020 and
OL,9,Fentered the King's Troop, Royal Horse
OL,10,FArtillery in June 2021.
OL,12,FThe soldier had been involved in
OL,13,Fceremonial operations with the troop
OL,14,Fincluding multiple Royal Gun Salutes
OL,15,Fin Hyde Park and Green Park, both in
OL,16,FLondon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
