FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1780434671
OL,3,CFuneral held for soldier who died at
OL,4,CRoyal Windsor Horse Show
OL,6,FThe MoD had said: "She was passionate
OL,7,Fabout everything to do with The Troop
OL,8,Fand participated in every extra
OL,9,Factivity available, including show
OL,10,Fjumping and The Troop Race."
OL,26,@nD@SOUrD@\O]
